                     <interp inst="t18250217-87-verdict514" type="verdictSubcategory" value="lesserOffence"></interp>
               GUILTY. Aged 30. Of Petty Larceny
            </rs>. - <rs id="t18250217-87-punish515" type="punishmentDescription">
